<div class="section-title">How it works.</div>
<p class="section-sub">From registration to delivery, three simple steps.</p>

<div class="service-grid">
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="step-number">1</div>
    <h3>Register</h3>
    <p>Our team logs your shipment and issues a tracking number instantly — no waiting for confirmation.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="step-number">2</div>
    <h3>Ship</h3>
    <p>Your package moves through our network by air, road, or ocean, with checkpoints logged along the way.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="step-number">3</div>
    <h3>Track</h3>
    <p>Check real-time status and current location anytime — no phone calls, no waiting on hold.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-title">Frequently asked questions.</div>
<p class="section-sub">Quick answers to the things shippers ask most.</p>

<div class="faq-list">
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>How do I get a tracking number?</summary>
    <p>Tracking numbers are issued by Pixel Wave staff when your shipment is registered. You'll receive it by email along with a reference number.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>What if my package is delayed?</summary>
    <p>Delays are logged as a status update with a note explaining what happened. You'll get an email the moment it's marked "Delayed," and can always check the live tracking page for the latest.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>Can I change the delivery address after registering?</summary>
    <p>Yes — contact our support team as soon as possible with your tracking number. Changes are easiest before a shipment is picked up.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>Do you ship internationally?</summary>
    <p>Yes, we move freight and parcels across 120+ countries by air, road, and ocean.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="faq-item">
    <summary>How do I contact support?</summary>
    <p>Use the Contact page, or email us directly at support@pixelwavelogistics.com.</p>
  </details>
</div>

